comments: Hunter (ATL) legally contests Herro's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Oladipo (MIA) moves somewhat laterally towards Murray (ATL) and marginal contact occurs at the end of the drive.
Oladipo (MIA) brushes Young's (ATL) off arm and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) and Butler (MIA) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the loose ball.
Oladipo (MIA) is jumping alongside Young's (ATL) path and marginal contact occurs as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Herro (MIA) is already in Hunter's (ATL) path when marginal contact occurs.  Additionally - Herro does not re-direct Young (ATL) into Hunter's path as he moves to navigate the pick.
Butler (MIA) moves laterally into Young's (ATL) path, delivering contact as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Murray (ATL) cleanly deflects the ball away from Herro (MIA).
Herro (MIA) is moving alongside Murray's (ATL) path and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) is already in Capela's (ATL) path and marginal contact occurs as the defenders switch.
Hunter (ATL) is drawn into the air on a pump fake towards Adebayo (MIA), and marginal contact occurs as Hunter jumps to Adebayo's side.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot, which he slides after his gather.
Capela (ATL) brings his lower half toward Martin (MIA) and marginal contact occurs during the screen.
Young (ATL) loses control of the ball on his own prior to any contact from Martin (MIA) or Butler (MIA).
Bey (ATL) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Adebayo (MIA) contests Murray's (ATL) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Bey (ATL) deflects the ball out of bounds.
Bey (ATL) commits a take foul on Oladipo (MIA).
After the missed free throw, Oladipo (MIA) interferes with the ball and prevents it from promptly being put back into play.
Hunter (ATL) does not inbound the ball within five seconds.
Vincent (MIA) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Murray (ATL) wraps Butler (MIA) off ball during the inbound.
